{"article_id":"UlmnMXCXal6WMp56","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"FERGUSON , Mo . --","depth":2},{"id":1,"text":"A white police officer will not face charges","depth":10},{"id":2,"text":"for fatally shooting an unarmed black teenager in a case","depth":11},{"id":3,"text":"that set off violent protests and racial unrest throughout the nation .","depth":11},{"id":4,"text":"A St. Louis County grand jury declined to indict officer Darren Wilson , 28 , for firing six shots in an August confrontation","depth":11},{"id":5,"text":"that killed 18-year-old Michael Brown ,","depth":11},{"id":6,"text":"St. Louis County prosecutor Robert McCulloch said Monday night .","depth":10},{"id":7,"text":"Crowds of protesters filled streets near the Ferguson police station","depth":11},{"id":8,"text":"following the announcement .","depth":11},{"id":9,"text":"A police car and stores were set on fire ,","depth":11},{"id":10,"text":"other stores were looted ,","depth":12},{"id":11,"text":"gunfire was heard","depth":13},{"id":12,"text":"and bricks were hurled .","depth":13},{"id":13,"text":"Police said","depth":12},{"id":14,"text":"they had been fired on and responded with smoke bombs and pepper spray","depth":13},{"id":15,"text":"before using tear gas .","depth":13},{"id":16,"text":"Police later said","depth":12},{"id":17,"text":"they came under heavy automatic weapon fire ,","depth":13},{"id":18,"text":"and some buildings were left to burn","depth":14},{"id":19,"text":"because of the danger .","depth":14},{"id":20,"text":"County police said","depth":11},{"id":21,"text":"an officer suffered a gunshot wound ,","depth":12},{"id":22,"text":"but it was unclear if it was because of the protest violence .","depth":12},{"id":23,"text":"Protests sprang up in cities from New York to Los Angeles","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"and remained mostly peaceful .","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"At least half a dozen commercial airline flights into St. Louis were diverted out of concerns about the unrest .","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"The Federal Aviation Administration at 11:15 p.m . ET said","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"it had restricted flights into and out of Lambert International Airport in St. Louis","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"to `` provide a safe environment for law enforcement activities . ''","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"The restriction lifts at 5:15 a.m . ET .","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"The grand jury 's decision had been long awaited","depth":6},{"id":31,"text":"and followed earlier Ferguson rioting","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"that resembled war-zone news footage in this predominantly black suburb of St. Louis .","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"In Washington , President Obama appeared before TV cameras .","depth":6},{"id":34,"text":"`` We need to accept","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"that this decision was the grand jury 's to make , ''","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"he said","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"in calling for peaceful protests .","depth":7},{"id":38,"text":"ButObama said","depth":6},{"id":39,"text":"the Ferguson case `` speaks to broader challenges","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"that we still face as a nation . ''","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"Prosecutor McCulloch made the announcement in an unusual nighttime presentation in a courtroom .","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"He spoke at length about media coverage of the case and what he called the unreliability of eyewitness accounts .","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"He said","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"the grand jury weighed evidence and testimony","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"before concluding","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"there was no probable cause","depth":12},{"id":47,"text":"to indict the officer .","depth":12},{"id":48,"text":"`` The duty of the grand jury is to separate fact from fiction , ''","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"McCulloch said .","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"He said","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"prosecuting attorneys presented five potential indictments to the grand jury ,","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"and all were rejected .","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"`` The jury was not inclined to indict on any charges , ''","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"Benjamin Crump , an attorney for Brown 's family , said","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"after being informed of the decision by authorities .","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"In grand jury testimony","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"released by prosecutors Monday night ,","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"Wilson , the officer , described the confrontation","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"and said","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"that Brown refused his instructions","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"to stop walking in the street .","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"He said","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"Brown cursed him ,","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"then slammed the officer 's car door shut","depth":12},{"id":65,"text":"as he was trying to exit his vehicle .","depth":12},{"id":66,"text":"He said","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"Brown appeared to be trying `` almost like to intimidate or overpower me . '' They scuffled","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"and Brown hit the officer ,","depth":12},{"id":69,"text":"Wilson testified .","depth":12},{"id":70,"text":"`` When I grabbed him ,","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"the only way","depth":14},{"id":72,"text":"I can describe it","depth":14},{"id":73,"text":"is","depth":13},{"id":74,"text":"I felt like a five-year-old","depth":13},{"id":75,"text":"holding Hulk Hogan , ''","depth":13},{"id":76,"text":"Wilson said .","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"He had no Taser weapon","depth":13},{"id":78,"text":"and felt","depth":14},{"id":79,"text":"his mace spray would not work ,","depth":14},{"id":80,"text":"Wilson said :","depth":12},{"id":81,"text":"`` So the only other option","depth":13},{"id":82,"text":"I thought","depth":14},{"id":83,"text":"I had","depth":14},{"id":84,"text":"was my gun . ''","depth":12},{"id":85,"text":"He drew it ,","depth":13},{"id":86,"text":"he said ,","depth":13},{"id":87,"text":"and told Brown to `` get back","depth":13},{"id":88,"text":"or I 'm going to shoot you . ''","depth":13},{"id":89,"text":"He said","depth":12},{"id":90,"text":"Brown grabbed the gun with his right hand","depth":13},{"id":91,"text":"and twisted it ,","depth":15},{"id":92,"text":"pushing it down into Wilson 's hip ,","depth":15},{"id":93,"text":"before the officer fired .","depth":14},{"id":94,"text":"Brown 's family attorneys received a call from McCulloch shortly before the announcement","depth":9},{"id":95,"text":"that there would be no charges against the officer .","depth":9},{"id":96,"text":"Crump took the call","depth":9},{"id":97,"text":"and and delivered the news to Brown 's family in an area hotel .","depth":9},{"id":98,"text":"Lesley McSpadden , Brown 's mother , cried and shouted","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"when Crump told her","depth":11},{"id":100,"text":"there was no indictment","depth":12},{"id":101,"text":"and that the prosecutor was willilng to meet with the family .","depth":12},{"id":102,"text":"McSpadden began crying and shouting .","depth":11},{"id":103,"text":"Her body vibrated with pain","depth":12},{"id":104,"text":"as she jumped to her feet .","depth":12},{"id":105,"text":"`` I do want to meet with him right now , ''","depth":12},{"id":106,"text":"McSpadden screamed .","depth":12},{"id":107,"text":"`` What do you mean no indictment ? ! ''","depth":11},{"id":108,"text":"She then ran out of a hotel room","depth":9},{"id":109,"text":"followed by family members .","depth":9},{"id":110,"text":"Brown 's family later released a statement","depth":8},{"id":111,"text":"saying ,","depth":9},{"id":112,"text":"`` We are profoundly disappointed","depth":10},{"id":113,"text":"that the killer of our child will not face the consequence of his actions . ''","depth":10},{"id":114,"text":"They urged others","depth":9},{"id":115,"text":"who share their pain","depth":9},{"id":116,"text":"to `` channel your frustration in ways","depth":9},{"id":117,"text":"that will make a positive change . ''","depth":9},{"id":118,"text":"Missouri Gov . Jay Nixon , a Democrat , called for calm","depth":9},{"id":119,"text":"after calling up National Guard troops","depth":10},{"id":120,"text":"to stand by in case of unrest .","depth":10},{"id":121,"text":"Speaking","depth":11},{"id":122,"text":"before the decision was announced ,","depth":11},{"id":123,"text":"he urged","depth":10},{"id":124,"text":"that `` regardless of the decision , people on all sides show tolerance , mutual respect and restraint . ''","depth":9},{"id":125,"text":"Crowds gathered around the Ferguson police headquarters in anticipation of the announcement at the courthouse in Clayton , Mo. , another St. Louis suburb .","depth":8},{"id":126,"text":"The 12-person grand jury had been considering","depth":11},{"id":127,"text":"whether probable cause existed","depth":12},{"id":128,"text":"to bring charges against Wilson , 28 , the white officer","depth":13},{"id":129,"text":"who fatally shot Brown , an 18-year-old black man , after their Aug. 9 confrontation .","depth":13},{"id":130,"text":"The shooting inflamed tensions in a largely minority community","depth":11},{"id":131,"text":"that is patrolled by an overwhelmingly white police force .","depth":11},{"id":132,"text":"Brown 's lifeless and bleeding body lay for more than four hours in a Ferguson residential street after the shooting ,","depth":11},{"id":133,"text":"prompting dismay and anger","depth":12},{"id":134,"text":"as a crowd gathered .","depth":12},{"id":135,"text":"Protests turned into rioting and looting the following night ,","depth":11},{"id":136,"text":"and police responded with armored vehicles and tear gas ,","depth":12},{"id":137,"text":"triggering a nationwide debate over police tactics .","depth":12},{"id":138,"text":"The grand jury ,","depth":12},{"id":139,"text":"including nine whites and three African Americans ,","depth":12},{"id":140,"text":"had been meeting in secret for months ,","depth":11},{"id":141,"text":"hearing evidence","depth":11},{"id":142,"text":"and weighing whether Wilson 's should face charges","depth":12},{"id":143,"text":"that could have ranged from involuntary manslaughter to murder .","depth":12},{"id":144,"text":"Brown 's family joined thousands of protesters","depth":11},{"id":145,"text":"to demand Wilson 's arrest in the weeks after the death of their son .","depth":11},{"id":146,"text":"As anger at official inaction grew","depth":12},{"id":147,"text":"following Brown 's death ,","depth":12},{"id":148,"text":"protesters clashed with police ,","depth":12},{"id":149,"text":"who began patrolling the streets with military-grade weapons and armored vehicles .","depth":12},{"id":150,"text":"Wilson has been on paid leave and largely invisible since the shooting .","depth":8},{"id":151,"text":"While the grand jury met in secret","depth":11},{"id":152,"text":"to hear evidence in the case ,","depth":11},{"id":153,"text":"two starkly different versions of the events","depth":12},{"id":154,"text":"leading to the shooting","depth":12},{"id":155,"text":"emerged in media accounts .","depth":11},{"id":156,"text":"Police have said","depth":12},{"id":157,"text":"a scuffle broke out","depth":13},{"id":158,"text":"after Wilson asked Brown and a friend to move out of the street .","depth":13},{"id":159,"text":"Wilson told investigators","depth":12},{"id":160,"text":"he shot Brown","depth":13},{"id":161,"text":"only after the teenager reached for the officer 's gun .","depth":13},{"id":162,"text":"Some witnesses said","depth":11},{"id":163,"text":"Brown had run away from Wilson ,","depth":12},{"id":164,"text":"then turned","depth":13},{"id":165,"text":"and raised his hands in the air in a gesture of surrender","depth":14},{"id":166,"text":"before he was shot in the head and chest .","depth":14},{"id":167,"text":"The unusual timing of the grand jury 's announcement ,","depth":12},{"id":168,"text":"after darkness had fallen ,","depth":12},{"id":169,"text":"was a decision of prosecutors ,","depth":11},{"id":170,"text":"Nixon said .","depth":10},{"id":171,"text":"St. Louis Mayor Francis Slay acknowledged","depth":11},{"id":172,"text":"the case `` has deeply divided us ''","depth":11},{"id":173,"text":"but said","depth":11},{"id":174,"text":"`` turning violent or damaging property will not be tolerated . ''","depth":11},{"id":175,"text":"The death of Brown touched off weeks of protests ,","depth":7},{"id":176,"text":"and the decision by the grand jury","depth":11},{"id":177,"text":"on whether to bring charges","depth":11},{"id":178,"text":"prompted extraordinary precautions by law enforcement and the community.","depth":10},{"id":179,"text":"The Ferguson school district canceled Tuesday classes .","depth":9},{"id":180,"text":"Wilson could still face civil rights charges","depth":10},{"id":181,"text":"brought by the Justice Department","depth":10},{"id":182,"text":"or a civil wrongful death lawsuit","depth":10},{"id":183,"text":"filed by Brown 's parents .","depth":10},{"id":184,"text":"Contributing :","depth":2},{"id":185,"text":"Brad Heath , Pete Eisler , ; KSDK-TV , St. Louis","depth":2}],"relations":[{"parent":371,"left":369,"right":370,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":369,"left":0,"right":368,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":368,"left":225,"right":367,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":225,"left":217,"right":224,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":217,"left":214,"right":216,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":214,"left":209,"right":213,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":209,"left":207,"right":208,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":207,"left":191,"right":206,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":191,"left":188,"right":190,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":188,"left":1,"right":187,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":187,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":190